                     !!! IMPORTANT WARNING !!!
Don't give userids and password of your own computer accounts to other
players! This means also any information about phone numbers for dialins
into your computer network or credit card numbers. If you have given your 
account to another player, e.g. Tyveris (aka Raver), please check with 
your system administrator if any security on your computer system was 
compromised, such as adding false root logins.
